{
  "stem": "24409.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Yes, he wanted-- only he wanted-- so many ways for me as a briber, for bribery, where they thought I was rich.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I think they wanted about $10 from me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I couldn't give him the $10.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I thought I put myself into the wrong.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I was absolutely kosher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I had nothing to declare.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So the others, of course, paid him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "From this I had learned my lesson in Romania.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "In Romania there was no intervention from the government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But the commander of the port, the police, the inspector, all wanted money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So the police inspector, I paid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I use always the same phrase.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I give it to you for charity, according to your own-- I give this for charity, according to your own disposition.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I give him-- I don't know anymore how much-- to the chief of police, and to bribe the port master.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was no problem with transferring.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said you can go through, but you cannot transfer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So transferring the people from the Danube ships to the and the and It was the first trip of the As you went through and did all these different things, how did you know who to trust?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You couldn't trust anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I had a confidence man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I was in my hotel room in Galati.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is about 30 or 40 miles from Bucharest on the Danube.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A man came in one morning with a fur coat, a little bit shabby, but very elegant, with fur collar and [INAUDIBLE], and a card on which was written John L.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Popesko, ?] Special Assistant to the Chief of Immigration of the Jews, and his phone number.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, what's that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, that's what I am.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
